10
00:00:23,140 --> 00:00:26,570
He’s the first president I remember as a
kid.

11
00:00:26,570 --> 00:00:28,750
In his years of service to the United States,

12
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:31,180
he accomplished a tremendous amount.

13
00:00:31,180 --> 00:00:33,260
And as a final accomplishment,

14
00:00:33,260 --> 00:00:34,370
at his funeral,

15
00:00:34,370 --> 00:00:36,780
